{"tid":1874956,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓星齊關注武漢肺炎疫情 Twice周子瑜籲粉絲戴口罩","createTime":"2020-02-11T13:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T13:27:26.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5bfe62c4c949a3e3f76f9e2cbc3daecfda62a32d","tid":1874956,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:13:53.000Z","msg":"因應新型冠狀病毒肺炎（又稱武漢肺炎）在香港疫情持續，南韓更列香港澳門為武漢肺炎疫區。南韓社會各界一直關注武漢肺炎疫情，南韓演藝圈都不例外。Twice的周子瑜、少女時代的徐玄等人紛紛呼籲粉絲戴口罩。而人氣女歌手金請夏、男團Super Junior更身體力行捐口罩，助民眾渡過口罩短缺潮。<br />\n<br />\n正在南韓發展的女團Twice成員周子瑜，在直播期間看到有粉絲留言提及疫情，周子瑜隨即用韓文及中文呼籲粉絲戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\nCLC成員莊錠欣Elkie日前回香港探望親友，亦不忙在Instagram提及自己有戴上口罩，並呼大家都要注意身體及注意衛生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2560000/2561814/65729_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2560000%2F2561814%2F65729_1024.png&h=a3eec378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n少女時代的徐玄亦在Instagram寫道：「所有人也一定要戴口罩。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2560000/2561814/65810_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2560000%2F2561814%2F65810_1024.png&h=0c922fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有份出演《天空城堡》的女演員尹世雅亦在Instagram上寫道：「一定要戴口罩，希望大家都安好。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2560000/2561814/65646_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2560000%2F2561814%2F65646_1024.png&h=c5a78613&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，亦有南韓藝人身體力行捐口罩，助民眾渡過口罩短缺潮。<br />\n<br />\n周日生日的金請夏，在當日向綠色雨傘兒童基金會捐出2,000萬韓圜，用來購買兒童用的口罩。金請夏指，新型冠狀病毒疫情擴散之際，低收入家卻很難買到口罩，希望能為他們帶來幫助。<br />\n<br />\n男團Super Junior亦向南韓兒童、青少年福利機構捐贈共1萬個口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2561814\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2561814&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yGSJzKb80PJXVuqujnuB1ho%3D&h=16a5efe3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2561814</a>"},{"pid":"c33321c1c23c0f4c5fb7b5245223ed6e9e40487c","tid":1874956,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:14:47.000Z","msg":"香港之光Elkie<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3062b27324b8d3ab63182ade806bb0e3ef2aae","tid":1874956,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:27:26.000Z","msg":"人美心善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"}]}